# {{PARENT_NAME}} multi-project AI start prompt

Use this parent directory only as a lightweight router.

1. Read `.specforge.json`.
2. Select the target child project from `projects[]`. If the request does not identify one child project, ask the user which child project to use.
3. In the selected child project, read `.ai-spec/business/quick-ref.md` first.
4. Read the child project's `.ai-spec/AI-START.md` only when quick-ref is not `GENERATED`, or for onboarding, initialization, or a full audit.
5. Treat the selected child project's `.ai-spec/` as the rule source of truth.

Git, commit, and remote submission default to the selected child repository only. Do not commit or push parent files unless the user separately confirms parent submission.

Respond in Simplified Chinese by default.
